name: Frantic fifteen Second Frog
description:
Jump. Jump! and JUMP! in this platformer. It is the only thing you can do. Reach the goal before the fifteen second timer runs out! Other wise... well you just restart the level. A lot trickier than it appears!

Controls:

Any key - Jump

Escape - Quit

Credits:

Music made in beepbox.co

Game made in Gamemaker Studio 2
